item.title: CVE-2021-25441|2024-08-03T20:03:05.752Z -- samsung%20mobile -- ar%20emoji%20editor
item.description: Improper input validation vulnerability in AR Emoji Editor prior to version 4.4.03.5 in Android Q(10.0) and above allows untrusted applications to access arbitrary files with an escalated privilege.
